      "title": "Modi assures PM Gunawardena of unwavering support",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi on Monday (1) assured newly elected Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena of India's continued support to the island nation in a congratulatory letter.",
        "He also expressed that he hopes Sri Lanka will witness quick economic recovery ensuring the prosperity and well-being of its people."
      ],
